 * 
</P>
<P>
 Add Notre Dame: Irish Coach Lou Holtz discounted any notion that Notre Dame 
now has a rivalry with Boston College. 
</P>
<P>
 "We don't have a rivalry with anyone except Southern Cal," he said. "Southern 
Cal is the only game we look forward to in the sense that it's a continuous 
rivalry." 
