<P>
UCLA, USC WOMEN VIE IN VOLLEYBALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The third-ranked UCLA women's volleyball team will play host to USC today at 
4:30 p.m. in a Pacific 10 Conference match at Pauley Pavilion. 
</P>
<P>
 The Bruins are 15-2 overall, 5-1 in conference play, and are led by Annett 
Buckner, who averages a Pac-10 leading 5.13 kills a game. The 11th-ranked 
Trojans (10-3, 4-2) are led by Vesna Dragicevic and Meika Wagner, who average 
3.7 kills a game. 
</P>
