 Gymnastics Classes to Begin on Oct. 21 
</P>
<P>
 Children can tumble their way through the fall in Placentia Community Services 
gymnastics classes, which begin Oct. 21. 
</P>
<P>
 The classes will be offered at Oberle Gym Stage, 974 S. Melrose Ave., through 
Dec. 6. 
</P>
<P>
 For more information, call the Community Services Department at (714) 
993-8232. 
