 Parking near the Santa Fe Express Cafe, Knowlwood Restaurant and other 
businesses around the downtown train station will soon be limited to one hour. 
</P>
<P>
 The City Council last week unanimously voted to convert 11 all-day parking 
spaces that are in front of the Santa Fe Express Cafe and 21 three-hour spaces 
next to Knowlwood's to one-hour slots. 
</P>
