Boulevard"; Jodi Carlisle, "Working"; Barbara Walsh, "Falsettos"; Carol 
Burnett, "Company" 
</P>
<P>
 * Featured Actor/Play: Patrick Kerr, "The End of the Day"; Eric Allan Kramer, 
"The Wood Demon"; Dakin Matthews, "The Wood Demon"; Cliff Jewell, 
"Misalliance"; Ellis E. Williams, "Distant Fires" 
</P>
<P>
 * Featured Actress/Play: Jane Elliot, "Last Summer at Bluefish Cove"; Lela 
Ivey, "The Waiting Room"; Maree Cheatham, "Last Summer at Bluefish Cove"; June 
