FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 CIA staffing -- Because of erroneous figures supplied by the Central 
Intelligence Agency, The Times reported incorrectly Monday that 20% of the 
agency's station chiefs were women as of last month. The CIA said Tuesday that 
only 8.4% of the station chiefs are women. 
